data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom tri-level home in Hobart! Home offers hardwood floors throughout and has plenty of living space. The upper level includes three bedrooms and a bathroom. The main level has a large great room with a kitchen and dining space. This home includes a screened in porch in the back and has a large fenced-in backyard. Home includes a newer furnace, hot water heater and new drain tile on the lower level. Don't miss you chance to see this home. Schedule your showing today!
